text: Renato Gaeta (born 24 April 1959) is an Italian rower. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Italy Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
